---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Meals & Facilities | Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura"
  description="Learn about the nutritious meals, spotless kitchen, and everyday facilities offered by Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Meals &amp; Facilities</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Residents of Jyoti Girls PG enjoy homely meals, clean utilities, and thoughtfully designed facilities that keep them energised through demanding study schedules.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Balanced Meals for Long Study Days</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Breakfast &amp; Morning Boosters</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Warm poha, upma, sprouts, and fruits served with brewed beverages ensure every student leaves for Osmanpura institutes on time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Nutritious Lunch &amp; Dinner</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Whole grains, seasonal vegetables, dal, and proteins form the core menu. Custom meals are planned for exam days or dietary needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Evening Snacks &amp; Hydration</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Light snacks, fresh juices, and herbal drinks refuel residents before evening study slots.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Kitchen &amp; Hygiene Standards</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Separate zones for chopping, cooking, and plating to avoid cross-contamination.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Weekly food safety audits with temperature control logs maintained by the head chef.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Hand-wash stations with motion sensors for staff and residents.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Food tasting log signed by the warden before every meal service.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Facility Upgrades for Everyday Comfort</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Housekeeping &amp; Laundry</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Rooms and bathrooms are cleaned daily, while laundry is handled twice a week with steam ironing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Power &amp; Connectivity</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Generator backup, inverter-supported study lamps, and high-speed Wi-Fi keep studies unaffected by outages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Recreation &amp; Wellness</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Indoor fitness equipment, reading lounges, and prayer rooms provide mindful breaks between coaching sessions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="visit">Book a meal tasting</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20can%20we%20schedule%20a%20mess%20visit%3F" class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request menu samples</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
